h.gjbof7l3hli">双语欢迎代理选择“ nijisanji en”河试镜</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2019/04/eff0ce2d30b2f10895b31c661549f1e3-kix.xsuujalwyvfn.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2019/04/eff0ce2d30b2f10895b31c661549f1e3-kix.xsuujalwyvfn-1024x576.png" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2019/04/eff0ce2d30b2f10895b31c661549f1e3-kix.xsuujalwyvfn-1024x576.png 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2019/04/eff0ce2d30b2f10895b31c661549f1e3-kix.xsuujalwyvfn-300x169.png 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2019/04/eff0ce2d30b2f10895b31c661549f1e3-kix.xsuujalwyvfn-768x432.png 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2019/04/eff0ce2d30b2f10895b31c661549f1e3-kix.xsuujalwyvfn-1536x864.png 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2019/04/eff0ce2d30b2f10895b31c661549f1e3-kix.xsuujalwyvfn.png 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><h3 id="h.zhq1qgtomhdh">申请条件</h3><blockquote><p>[必需的]<br />・首次亮相后，可能的积极活动至少12个月或更长时间是我作为彩流器的经验・创建一个视频，从此处指定的选项中扩展故事。<br />・日语和英语的双语・除了日语和英语外，那些会说不同语言的人</p><p>申请表：https： <a href="https://forms.gle/Vu7P1sNcYKvFRQwSA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">//forms.gle/vu7p1sncykvfrqwsa</a></p></blockquote><h2 id="h.gknt5d2m6sga">日程</h2><p>申请期：从2023年11月17日（星期五） -  12月11日（星期一）12:00</p><p> “虚拟人才学院（VTA）”试听选择时间表：<br />・主要选择：文档筛选 /次要选择：呼叫访谈 /能力测试：Web测试 /最终选择：在东京或大阪的访谈</p><p>双语欢迎代理选择“ nijisanji en”河试听选择时间表：<br />・主要选择：文档筛选 /次要选择：致电面试 /最终选择：呼叫面试</p><h2 id="h.a8ud7u4wxeog">VTA相关文章</h2><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/10/pastedimage0-404c908b2e8e33bc9877589effb42440-kix.xl2z3xfi38r6-300x169.png"></div><div class="card-body mg-card-text p-2 p-lg-3"><h3 class="h6 mt-0 mw-0 mb-1 p-0 card-title mg-card-title mg-text-break-all text-dark font-weigh